#Lua SEXPs

$Operator: lua-count-turrets
$Category: Status
$Subcategory: Weapons, Shields, and Engines
$Minimum Arguments: 1
$Maximum Arguments: 2
$Return Type: Number
$Description: Returns an the number of turrets left of a particular ship.
$Parameter:
	+Description: The ship to check
	+Type: Ship
$Parameter:
	+Description: Which weapon the turret needs to carry at least one of to count. Counts all turrets by default.
	+Type: String
	
#End